summary: Ant-Man and The Wasp Star Evangeline Lilly Pitches Avengers Movie Idea!
title: Ant-Man and The Wasp Star Evangeline Lilly Pitches Avengers Movie Idea!
body:
Ant-Man and The Wasp Star Evangeline Lilly Pitches Avengers Movie Idea!

Ant-Man and The Wasp star Evangeline Lilly recently spoke with PopBuzz about her ideas for the future of the Avengers.

Specifically Lilly pitched an all-female Avengers team. And she also made her choice about who she thinks should lead the team. She chose Brie Larson’s Captain Marvel.

Lilly would explain why she chose Captain…

summary: Marvel fans, traumatized after Infinity War and waiting for Captain Marvel to come out: It's ok it's fine we're getting a...
body:
Marvel fans, traumatized after Infinity War and waiting for Captain Marvel to come out: It’s ok it’s fine we’re getting a Captain Marvel movie and then she’ll save the day in Avengers 4 and everything will be FINE

Marvel probably, constantly trying to mess with everyone: “-and then once they think there’s hope we turn her to dust in the post-credit scene”

summary: So when my sister found it last night that the Fifth was National Sisters Day, we started work on a pop-up card for me…that was...
caption:
So when my sister found it last night that the Fifth was National Sisters Day, we started work on a pop-up card for me…that was Captain Marvel themed. She looked up videos on how to make pop-ups and everything, I’m so proud—this is all legit from scratch.

So I bought her a large coke icee and popcorn chicken in return this morning.
